data.description: Gorgeous Executive Milton Home located in the highly sought-after Champions View Subdivision! Beautiful private lot surrounded by hardwood trees, offering a fabulous backyard oasis, large deck for grilling and entertaining, and situated on a quiet cul-de-sac street. The gorgeous gourmet kitchen highlights high-end custom blue cabinets with commercial grade double oven, stainless appliances, and a coffee station-butler's pantry with gorgeous quartz countertops and glass cabinet doors. The kitchen boasts a cozy breakfast area room with a beautiful view of the private backyard and is open to the great room with 2 story ceiling, fireplace, and wall of windows! The charming entry foyer is bright and open to the elegant formal dining room, and a combination library and music room. There is a guest suite on the main that is currently used as an office and an updated full bath for guests! Hardwood floors grace the main floor. There are front and rear stairs that lead to the second floor. The second floor boasts a grand owner's suite with separate his and her closets & and a freshly updated custom spa-like bath that offers dual vanities, tiled walk-in shower, glass window above the large soaking tub, quartz countertops, and marble tile floors. There are three additional bedrooms with one being a junior owner suite and two additional baths. Not to be missed is the terrace level which can accommodate a separate living space with a separate private entrance. This space offers a second kitchen, a guest suite and full bath, a media room, an entertainment room with a bar. There is a cozy wine cellar and a huge game closet. Finishing out the terrace level are French doors leading out to a flagstone patio with grilling area and accented by a fabulous garden trellis. This is a swim-tennis community that offers lightning fast AT&T fiber optic cable, located minutes to GA 400, plenty of shopping and restaurants, and some of the best public and private schools in the state!
